  "finalSubmissionGuidelines": "<div class=\"previewMask\">\n<div class=\"previewMask\">\n<div class=\"previewMask\">\n<div class=\"previewMask\">\n<div class=\"previewMask\">\n<h2><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">Submission Deliverables</span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\n\n<p><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">Below is an overview of the deliverables:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Shell scripts for heorku deployment</li>\n\t<li><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">A complete and detailed deployment documented (github wiki page) explaining how to deploy the application including configuration information.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n\t<li>The heroku url where you deploy the arena web.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">Final Submission</span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\n\n<p><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span class=\"small_info_spec\" id=\"rswGuidelines\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">For each member, the final submission should be uploaded to the Online Review Tool.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
